snippet.title: Kiwi: Airborne | 2D Side Scroller (with Godot)
snippet.description:
Kiwi: Airborne, is a 2D side-scroller, made with Godot, in which you help a Kiwi fulfill its dream of flight, all while attempting to overcome the various obstacles in its way; made for the 2020 Open Jam in a weekend, inspired by the short film Kiwi!


Entry: https://itch.io/jam/open-jam-2020/rate/764363
GitHub: https://github.com/ClarkThyLord/Kiwi-Airborne
